                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 EAC/11–844: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hyde Park</hi>, N.Y.</placeName>] <date
                            calendar="gregorian" when="1944-11-08">November 8,
                        1944</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Approve French Membership on European Advisory Commission to be announced
                    November 11th, but this should be so worded as to make advisory character of
                    Commission clear.</p>
            </div>
